C.H.I.P Computer (http://nextthing.co)
  connected to
PervasiveDisplays EPD extension board-05 (http://repaper.org/tools.html)


Pinout:
      Display     | CHIP      | CHIP PRO
  ------------------------------------
    1 VCC         | VCC-3V3   | VCC-3V3
    7 SPI_CK      | CSICK     | CSI-MCLK
    8 BUSY        | CSID6     | CSID6
   10 /RESET      | CSID7     | CSID7
   11 PANEL_ON    | CSID4     | CSID4
   12 DISCHARGE   | CSID2     | CSID2
   13 BORDER_CTRL | CSID0     | CSID0
   14 SPI_MISO    | CSIVSYNC  | CSIVSYNC
   15 SPI_MOSI    | CSIHSYNC  | CSIHSYNC
   18 FLASH_CS    | VCC-3V3   | VCC-3V3
   19 /EPD_CS     | CSIPCK    | CSI-MCLK
   20 GND         | GND       | GND
